                    <a href="game-picker.html" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.875rem 2rem; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0.75rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #4f46e5);">🎯 今晚玩什麼？</a>
